________________________________________________________________________

UEAnalysisRootupleProducer.cc
________________________________________________________________________

Author: Florian Bechtel (florian.bechtel@desy.de)
Purpose: Convert hepmc files to UEAnalysis rootuples

Dependencies:
	Needs installations of HepMC, HepPDT, Fastjet, Root
	You can use e.g. the GENSER installation at CERN
________________________________________________________________________

How to:
	To compile, invoke 'make UEAnalysisRootupleProducer'
	To run, invoke './UEAnalysisRootupleProducer'

Notes:

- Analysis assumes input file to be called "infile"
  You can either set a soft link or rename your input 
  (or you change the relevant lines in UEAnalysisRootupleProducer.cc)

________________________________________________________________________

